<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About Me</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <h1><%= title %></h1>
    </header>

    <!-- Navigation Bar -->
    <nav>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
        <li><a href="/projects">Projects</a></li>
        <% if (authenticated) { %>
          <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
          <li>
            <form action="/logout" method="POST">
              <button type="submit">Logout</button>
            </form>
          </li>
        <% } %>
      </ul>
    </nav>

    <main>
      <!-- Profile Image -->
      <img
        src="/images/my-image.jpg"
        alt="Kawaljeet Kaur"
        style="width: 250px; height: auto; border-radius: 50%"
      />

      <h2>About Me</h2>
      <p>
        I'm Kawaljeet Kaur, a recent graduate from the Software Systems Developer program at BCIT.
        I hold a Bachelor's in Computer Applications and a Bachelor's in Education, combining
        technical expertise with strong communication and teaching skills.
      </p>

      <p>
        Over the past year, I’ve built several full-stack applications using technologies like
        HTML, JavaScript, React, Angular, Vue, C#, Node.js, Express, MongoDB, and AWS. I enjoy
        solving real-world problems through code and continuously learning new tools and frameworks.
      </p>

      <p>
        Whether it’s backend logic, frontend design, or cloud deployment — I love creating smooth,
        impactful user experiences. My goal is to join a dynamic team where I can grow as a developer
        and contribute to meaningful projects.
      </p>

      <!-- Social Media Links -->
      <p>Connect with me on:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="<%= linkedIn %>" target="_blank"><strong>LinkedIn</strong></a></li>
        <li><a href="<%= Github %>" target="_blank"><strong>GitHub</strong></a></li>
      </ul>
    </main>

    <footer>&copy; 2025 Kawaljeet Kaur</footer>
  </body>
</html>
